  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Venture into the heart of darkness with <strong>PHOTOBIA: Tales from the Dark</strong>, an indie puzzle game built around the manipulation of light and time. Explore shadowy labyrinths, uncover hidden secrets, and bend reality to your will.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919230/extras/d95f8b066ad1a2c6d8f3ac33a5cd4c42.avif?t=1755427738\" width=640 height=128 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a universe where light becomes a tool of power, solve multidimensional puzzles and alter the flow of time to move beyond the unknown. Every reflection hides a clue.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919230/extras/554afeb939464f4206a6b7f32899b624.avif?t=1755427738\" width=640 height=128 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with light to reshape your surroundings and use physics to your advantage. Overcome increasingly complex challenges in a world that constantly shifts around you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919230/extras/30332ab17a67cd43265288d02ecaf9bd.poster.avif?t=1755427738\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919230/extras/30332ab17a67cd43265288d02ecaf9bd.webm?t=1755427738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919230/extras/30332ab17a67cd43265288d02ecaf9bd.mp4?t=1755427738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919230/extras/863afd61d4481f748ab4dff30e52fea6.poster.avif?t=1755427738\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919230/extras/863afd61d4481f748ab4dff30e52fea6.webm?t=1755427738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919230/extras/863afd61d4481f748ab4dff30e52fea6.mp4?t=1755427738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919230/extras/2461294f7984ad2eac8b3322d980f50b.avif?t=1755427738\" width=640 height=128 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transcend the boundaries of what’s possible as you master the manipulation of space and time. Each puzzle offers a new opportunity to interact with a realm where reality bends to your will.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919230/extras/c1926d5357fdec033e8ce7cdeff1a55b.poster.avif?t=1755427738\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919230/extras/c1926d5357fdec033e8ce7cdeff1a55b.webm?t=1755427738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919230/extras/c1926d5357fdec033e8ce7cdeff1a55b.mp4?t=1755427738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919230/extras/f3b60768e561eecbe7faa0d0d2c78e33.avif?t=1755427738\" width=640 height=128 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An ancient mystery lies hidden in the shadows. Progress through increasingly intricate levels, uncover fragments of truth, and unravel a riddle that transcends the very understanding of the dark realm.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Escape</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world around you is collapsing. Traverse unstable labyrinths and use every skill at your disposal to stay one step ahead of reality’s disintegration.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hardcore</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time is short and the shadows are more hostile than ever. Only those who master the manipulation of light will overcome the most extreme trials of this twisted realm.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Permadeath</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No room for mistakes. A single misstep and the darkness will consume you forever. Face the most unforgiving challenge, where mercy does not exist.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Speedrun</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race against the clock and compete with players from around the world. Sharpen your reflexes, master the light, and claim the title of ultimate speedrunner in the dark realm.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sandbox</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash your creativity in the Steam Workshop. Design new levels, share your creations, and explore community-made worlds in a universe that constantly expands.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Playroom</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge up to four players in a series of fast-paced, ever-changing minigames where speed, cunning, and skill decide the winner.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Venture into the heart of darkness with <strong>PHOTOBIA: Tales from the Dark</strong>, an indie puzzle game built around the manipulation of light and time. Explore shadowy labyrinths, uncover hidden secrets, and bend reality to your will.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919230/extras/d95f8b066ad1a2c6d8f3ac33a5cd4c42.avif?t=1755427738\" width=640 height=128 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a universe where light becomes a tool of power, solve multidimensional puzzles and alter the flow of time to move beyond the unknown. Every reflection hides a clue.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919230/extras/554afeb939464f4206a6b7f32899b624.avif?t=1755427738\" width=640 height=128 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with light to reshape your surroundings and use physics to your advantage. Overcome increasingly complex challenges in a world that constantly shifts around you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919230/extras/30332ab17a67cd43265288d02ecaf9bd.poster.avif?t=1755427738\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919230/extras/30332ab17a67cd43265288d02ecaf9bd.webm?t=1755427738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919230/extras/30332ab17a67cd43265288d02ecaf9bd.mp4?t=1755427738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><vi