738\" width=640 height=128 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An ancient mystery lies hidden in the shadows. Progress through increasingly intricate levels, uncover fragments of truth, and unravel a riddle that transcends the very understanding of the dark realm.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Escape</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world around you is collapsing. Traverse unstable labyrinths and use every skill at your disposal to stay one step ahead of reality’s disintegration.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hardcore</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time is short and the shadows are more hostile than ever. Only those who master the manipulation of light will overcome the most extreme trials of this twisted realm.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Permadeath</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No room for mistakes. A single misstep and the darkness will consume you forever. Face the most unforgiving challenge, where mercy does not exist.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Speedrun</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race against the clock and compete with players from around the world. Sharpen your reflexes, master the light, and claim the title of ultimate speedrunner in the dark realm.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sandbox</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash your creativity in the Steam Workshop. Design new levels, share your creations, and explore community-made worlds in a universe that constantly expands.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Playroom</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge up to four players in a series of fast-paced, ever-changing minigames where speed, cunning, and skill decide the winner.</p>",
